column5: Well it was a great start to 2017. I haven't touched a rod since August. Way too long. Anyways turned out to be a great start to the year. We managed to land double digit numbers of Whitefish and even managed a Laker to end the day. Forgot my jacket in the truck so was a bit chilly. Got fish on 5 different colors of jigs today. Found them in 87 to 92 fow.  Was tough jigging in the white caps at times but was a fun few hours out.
you're killing me  nice catch
you're killing me  nice catch  What he said!  James... you got us jonzing!  Some great fishing and feel required from a rocking boat for whiteys at those depths. Well done again!
Thanx for reporting.  Strange - I had to look twice when I saw the pic of your truck & boat in the driveway, with all that snow!
Awesome
very nice!
Awesome, great job.  Figured Simcoe would have had a skim by now at least.
Woah! Great haul!
Why wernt we all invited to the party.?
Whooda thought January?,nice haul !!!!!!!
Sweet !
Sweet dude.  Thanks for the call. Rethinking now, I should of went out today.  How did ya make out?  Lots of guys out this morning.

I hate writing "nice fish" over and over so I am going to say Fantasmic. Is it legal to use the "ice fishing" grip on the rod even if there isn't any ice?  Do you have snow tires on the trailer? I towed the boat in the snow once and will never do that again, ever. A nightmare when a storm hit on the 400.
We are all 5-10 minutes, from Simcoe launches.  Alot of toon launches, are even closer.
Great way to ring in the new year !
Hey Brian, Happy New year bud. I have done much damage in 5 miles driving. I totalled a car 4 doors from where I lived once.
I'm 6 min from the launch and I got good new rubber on the trailer. Not much snow if any on the roads.. just the ramp.

Absolutely, positively, freakin' INCREDIBLE.  I did three double takes when I saw the boat and open water.  Unbelievable.  and AWESOME.  Well done!!!!  Doug  (wishing I still lived down that way reading this report...............)
Wow!
Alot of toon launches, are even closer.  So what's your excuse for not being out in your toon?? You don't plan on having any more kids anyway, do you??
